results.deck: Nitro Games is a Finnish game developer.
results.description: They have created naval and trading strategy games East India Company (2009) and Commander: Conquest of the Americas (2010) . Their latest release is the arcadey PC game Woody Two-Legs: Attack of the Zombie Pirates. They are also working on the PC port of Alan Wake together with a small team from Remedy.
